Class BasicInventory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.voxelgameslib.voxelgameslib.components.inventory.BaseInventory
      • com.voxelgameslib.voxelgameslib.components.inventory.BasicInventory

  • public class BasicInventory
extends BaseInventory
    A basic inventory is a type of inventory.

    It has only one page. Clicking an item will perform an action. There will be no extra pages other than the single inventory page.
